__________________________________________________
##### Basic Calculation 2 digits to 6 digits Only
__________________________________________________


===>>>Examples: 1) Input section:

		import simplecalculate as se
		a = se.add(6,8) #add two values
		print(a)

		b = se.subtract4(4,5,6,5) #subtract Four values
		print(b)

		c = se.add6(4,10,5,9,8,2) #add six values
		print(c)

		d = se.add6(4,10,5,9,8,2,2) #add seven values
		print(d)

		Output section:
		14
		-12
		38
		error
